<!-- Section 6 — Origin Story -->
<section class="section-origin">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="section-origin__inner">
      <span class="section-origin__label">THE BEGINNING</span>
      <h2 class="section-origin__headline">A Door. A New Name. A Mandate.</h2>
      <p class="section-origin__text">At six, our founder was adopted. Every system after that door treated him like a case number. Foster care. Public school. Mental health services. All built around young people, none built <em>with</em> them.</p>
      <p class="section-origin__text">So he built the thing that didn't exist. AHG is the answer to every room that decided his future without asking his name.</p>
      <a href="/about" class="btn btn-outline btn-outline--light">READ THE FULL STORY</a>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

